title: Frayt: Anything Delivered
description:
Frayt is an on demand shipping and delivery service that helps businesses and individuals ship anything, anywhere. 

Once matched, our professional drivers will come to you in 59 minutes or less, help you load your item, and deliver your package to its destination. Frayt's fleet of drivers offer any size of vehicle including trucks, cargo vans, and box trucks (coming soon!) to handle anything from a parcel to a 3,000 lb pallets.

With this app, you can quickly connect with Frayt drivers 24/7, 7 days a week. Need shipping from store to home, store to store, home to home, warehouse to store or distribution center to contractors - Frayt has you covered.


WHY BUSINESSES AND INDIVIDUALS LOVE FRAYT -

Within the Hour Pickup.
With 100s of drivers in 30+ major markets, just enter the pickup and delivery destination in the app and we will be there in 59 minutes or less!

Frayt is now available in Atlanta, Akron, Albany, Charlotte, Chicago, Cincinnati, Cleveland, Columbus, Dayton, Flint, Denver, Detroit, Fort Lauderdale, Fort Wayne, Grand Rapids, Indianapolis, Lexington, Long Island, Louisville, Miami, Michigan City, Nashville, New Your City, Oklahoma City, Orlando, Philadelphia, Pittsburgh, South Bend, Syracuse, Tampa, Toledo, and Youngstown.

Small or Big - we've got you covered.
Unlike the other guys, the Frayt fleet includes CARS/COURIERS, CARGO VANS, PICKUP/MIDSIZE TRUCKS, and BOX TRUCKS (coming soon!) to handle the big stuff like hardware, tile, etc.

Quality, Professional Drivers.
The Frayt fleet up holds a strict policies to ensure that our drivers follow industry standards. Each driver must pass a national background check and MVR check.

No-contact delivery available.
We make sure to keep you and your customers safer. Just take a picture to confirm delivery - no contact needed.

On Demand, 24/7 365 days!
Don't worry what the time, day, or location. We will ensure we have a professional driver available to pickup and deliver when you need it.

LIVE Tracking
Once your item has been picked up, the Frayt App gives you real-time notifications so you know where your item is and when it gets delivered.


Frayt wants to change how package-deliveries are done. We strive to improve last mile and local deliveries by providing same day delivered for individuals and business owners, so they can check one less thing on their to-do list. 

Frayt is also the best delivery & shipping partner for growing businesses. We help your business expand its reach and increase its sales by offering urgent, same-day, and next-day delivery for less. We help Retailers, Distributors, Service companies and Service Techs with instant and best express shipping solutions. Our happy customers include online shopping portals, offline stores, food delivery outlets and many more. Frayt also helps you with your retail and e-commerce business. We help growing companies compete with big companies, allowing you to ship the same day just like your competitors. We help you save money by minimizing your assets and taking care of everything for you.
releaseNotes: New layout and design and a much faster app!
